FAQ s | The FĒNX Launch Resources NC Grind About About FAQs Contact Sign In Select Page Home FAQs Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs) Incolo helps founders scale off fit, develop compelling positioning, train on how to go after funding opportunities, and cultivate a community of partners and other entrepreneurs to help them Founders Seeking Investment FAQs What are the most common questions founders should ask before pursuing investors? What is Investment Crowdfunding? What is Investment Crowdfunding? Investment crowding is a funding vehicle to raise capital from community, customers, professional investors, and other supporters of Similarly to an investor working directly with a founder to invest, investment crowdfunding elevates that relationship by using the power of technology for investors to transparently view different business online in one location and determine what businesses they want to invest in based on a compelling business Investment crowdfunding offers the flexibility to democratize investing by using any securities exemption strategy (accredited or investors) to facilitate the raise process in a way that is efficient and effective for both founders and the Is investment crowdfunding similar to Kickstarter and Indiegogo? Is it a nonprofit that gives grants to companies? How does investment crowdfunding work? Is similar to Kickstarter and Indiegogo? Is it a nonprofit that gives grants to companies? It’s not, but it is similar to Kickstarter because it provides an online platform for people to choose to put money in However unlike with Kickstarter where a person would get just a reward, perk or gift for contributing to an early stage B2C company campaign, investment crowdfunding allows both B2B and B2C companies to seek investors for their In a Rev Share, the company is paying investors off top line In an equity offering your community of investors have stake in your Investment crowdfunding is not a nonprofit that provides grants or What are the benefits of investment crowdfunding? What are the benefits of investment crowdfunding? Unlike the offline raise process, Investment Crowdfunding provides a business the ability to make a raise strategy match a founder’s business strategy, not the other way The founders get to choose which investor base they are making an offering to and what the terms will be to each investor They can create equity and or debt offerings, and work with advisors to determine the terms of the CrowdfundNC facilitates investment crowdfunding with three main principles: Community: Certain raises are idea for running a crowdfunding campaign where people come together to mass support a business, further supporting the regional Accessibility: Investment crowdfunding supports access to capital for founders and investors, letting them set the terms of how much they want to raise and Flexibility: The investment crowdfunding model provides a variety of options to meet founders and investors CrowdfundNC’s launch readiness advisory services and partnership with Localstake helps guide their business through the decision What does it take to launch an investment raise on platform? What does it take to launch an investment raise on platform? Whether a founder is raising privately or publicly, foundationally, it’s about compelling business Funding follows a compelling story, solid traction points for the stage of the business, and a sound operational Our “Investability Guide” provides founders with the foundational elements needed to entangle their business and funding In the end whether a founder ends up raising investment capital is up to We’ve had more founders grow off revenue than investment Note: We are not a Broker Dealer, Funding Platform, or Investment We do not provide funding and don’t structure How much capital has been raised through investment crowdfunding? How much capital has been raised through investment crowdfunding? Investment crowdfunding has been used by thousands of entrepreneurs across the country even more so Some of the latest statistics for the US (as of April ): $4B+ of investment capital raised since Over $368M has been raised from mostly investors leveraging Regulation Crowdfunding (Ref CF) since From : $107.9M raised $121.3M raised in , a % increase over ($75.8M) Does CrowdfundNC only support investment crowdfunding for North Carolina investors and businesses? Does CrowdfundNC only support investment crowdfunding North Carolina investors and businesses? While most of our founders are based in North Carolina, CrowdfundNC also supports businesses which have an impact on North Also, businesses can seek investors across the We believe having a regional focus enhances the capital raising experience so community can come together to support businesses they know, love and What is an accredited investor? What is an accredited investor? An accredited investor is usually defined as a person who has $1M in net assets (not including their primary residence), or a gros

extra layer of scrutiny regarding responsible business Investment Management : Tactical Allocations We follow economic and market trends and tilt the portfolio weightings in an effort to take advantage of opportunities or reduce risks in the ​ Investment Management : ​ Portfolios are annually, as market swings cause the portfolios weightings to drift too far from targets, and as targets Here s the official statute and here’s the statute in a Google document where you can ask questions and provide Briefly, the CCPA says a business must: Disclose in its privacy policy consumers rights under the CCPA, including the right to opt out of the information sales, how to submit consumer requests, and a list of the categories of personal information collected, sold and disclosed about consumers in the preceding Deliver the personal information they collected about the consumer in response to a “verifiable consumer ” Delete the personal information they collected about a consumer and direct their vendors (“service providers”) to delete it as well, in response to a verifiable consumer Display a "Do Not Sell My Personal Information" link on their homepage that enables consumers to opt out of the sale of the consumer s personal Display a number that consumers can call to register privacy And the CCPA says businesses must not: Discriminate against a consumer who exercises their CCPA rights (but they can charge different prices or provide goods or services in certain circumstances). Sell personal information of consumers known to be less than years of age, unless the consumer, if aged to years, or the consumer s parent or guardian, for consumers under , has affirmatively authorized the Does CCPA apply to me? The CCPA applies to for profit businesses that are “doing business” in California and that do one of the following: Have $25 million in revenue (likely from all jurisdictions, although the CCPA is ambiguous on this point) or Buys, receives, sells, or shares personal information about ,000 or more consumers, households, or devices (if your website serves ,000 or more unique visitors, you’ve likely collected sufficient analytics data) or Derives = % of annual revenue from selling CA consumers’ personal information (this is probably most relevant to data brokers and other marketing or ad tech businesses). “Doing business” in California can include entering into repeated transactions within California, maintaining a physical presence in California such as offices or servers, and having employees in It is possible for a bu

were developed originally for the people supported in the residential programs and further expanded into vocational and supported employment offerings for members of the For more than years we have While this was not a item for expectant mothers, we did find a great deal of support and excitement amongst providers (especially those in rural areas), and national organizational leaders as they view our solution as yet another effort aimed at mortality reduction via improved access to Founders Hector Torres, CEO Commercialization expert, who has helped several biomedical companies matriculate from infancy to robust solutions both in the US, as well as Latin Torres has a BAS Degree in Computer Science from Davenport University and a Master of Science in Technology development in medicine, and leadership experience in successfully moving biomedical to Haeri is an (OB-GYN) specialized in pregnancy and Haeri dedicated more than years of his carrier serving in the Army Reserve where he retired as Major Medical Find out more Thomas Milner Distinguished professor in biomedical engineering, with numerous grants and patents for various biomedical devices with a focus on optical sensors, who also has led the development of several devices from to Milner is a professor of engineering in the Department of Biomedical Engineering at the University of Texas at Austin, he was named UT Inventor of the Year in November Find out more The Problem Giving birth is one of the most dangerous things a woman can Out of every ,000 live births, results in maternal morbidity, but this statistic fails to convey how dangerous birth can be for mothers in developing While worldwide maternal mortality rates are slowly declining, the risk of maternal mortality skyrockets in rural or developing areas, where complications pose a more substantial and widespread countries and communities comprise a disproportionate % of maternal mortalities, and the rate of maternal mortality has continued to rise rather than The most common cause of maternal mortality is postpartum hemorrhage (PPH). Having your home inspected annually helps identify issues and defects in the home that can become all to easy to overlook as we walk past them every This abbreviated inspection looks at the following: exterior of the home for signs of water intrusion, exterior water management, exhaust terminals, exterior faucets, sump system, Smoke & CO alarms, plumbing system for leaks, combustion analysis of furnace, venting of furnace water heater, and your The end result is a report with images, similar to our home inspection reports, that you can use to get your home in SCHEDULE AN ANNUAL PROPERTY REVIEW A STANDARD HOME INSPECTION INCLUDES: SO WHAT EXACTLY IS A HOME INSPECTION? EXTERIOR INTERIOR A home inspection is an objective, visual inspection of the physical structure and systems of the The inspection will arm you with detailed, unbiased We ll uncover building defects, necessary repairs, potential safety hazards, and preventative maintenance issues that could cost you a lot of money down the We ll also help you understand which issues are major, and which problems can be corrected Roof if accessible and visible, we check the roof covering materials, gutters & downspouts, vents, chase & chimney, flashing, and any other roof Foundation we check for possible foundation failure, indicated by cracks or Exterior Walls we check for damaged or missing siding, cracks, and excessive soil contact which can be an invitation for Grading we check to ensure that the ground slopes away from the house, which helps to prevent water from entering the house or causing damage to the

CUSTODIAL ROTH IRA S - OOH LA LA Home Team CFA Blog More All Posts Search Log in Sign up Stephen Mulholland, CFA Sep 2 min read CUSTODIAL ROTH IRA S - OOH LA LA “I wish that I knew what I know now when I was younger,” Faces, Ooh La La If you are under , enterprising, and generating income you should have a Roth While you cannot have a until you are , thanks to Congressman William Roth s actions in you can open a Roth H ere are the basics: After tax contributions can be withdrawn tax and penalty free anytime Earnings can be used for college and graduate school tax and penalty free anytime $10,000 of your earnings can be used tax and penalty free to purchase a home Earnings can be drawn penalty and tax free after In you can put away up to $6,000 a year The contributions have to come from activities that generate earned income: lifeguard at a water amusement park (my first job at ) a paid internship baby sitting washing cars Everyone knows the power of savings, compounding, and deferring However, not everyone takes full advantage of the menu of investment The biggest reason why is probably the somewhat mistaken notion that you cannot touch the money until you re So, for the rest of this post I will try and help you to see that this isn t the Let s say you work from to and put $6,000 a year into your Roth At , you would have a little over $100,000 in contributions that you could use for any Jeff Bezos asked his parents for $300,000 at to start Luckily for his family they had the cash and You can fund a third of that for yourself just out of your Not everyone is as lucky as Jeff to have parents that can write those kinds of Why not your future business venture yourself? Alternatively, you can put that $100,000 towards a And that is just what you can do with the You would still have all of the earnings that $100,000 in contributions generated continuing to grow for Further, if you decide to go to graduate school you can use any portion of your Roth to fund it and stay out of crippling student There are myriad reasons people don t do For me, the saddest one is when they simply don t even know it s If you are a young, hard working person, or a parent of one, now you know! Estate Planning & Administration - Mazzella Estate & Asset Management Special Offer for New Clients (480) Home About Us Introduction Why Fee Based Advisors Disclosures (ADV) Services Estate Planning & Administration Retirement Planning Investment Management Insurance Analysis Tax Mitigation Strategies Business & Executive Benefits Medicare Information Client Portal Blog Contact Us Select Page Estate Planning & Administration If you are wondering if you need Estate Planning, we should first define the term which means different things to different In our definition Estate Planning would encompass everything we own and what we want done for ourselves if we are incapable of doing it Using that definition everyone needs some amount of Estate Of course, many people have no plans at all leaving major decisions about their assets, health care, and final wishes up to the At a minimum an individual and couples should have the following legal documents: Will Living Will Medical Power of Attorney Durable General Power of Attorney However, in many cases a Will by itself is not After all it is just a ticket to Probate is unpredictable because your will can be challenged, it can be lengthy (some probate cases have taken years!), and very To avoid the negative results of a will alone some clients might benefit more from a Revocable Living Trust (RLT). An RLT not only avoids probate but also gives the grantors control of the assets even after they have The RLT is part of a complete Estate Plan which includes your Will, Living Will, Medical Power of Attorney, Durable General Power of Attorney, and other estate planning While MEAM does not practice law, we do work with strategic partners who are either Estate Planning Attorneys and or Certified Document Preparers appointed by the Arizona Supreme These strategic partners can help advise on the best combination of estate planning documents for your Estate Administration As a client of MEAM we are relied upon to help fulfill the estate plan working with your trustee or power of attorney Initially our role is to help with the proper titling of assets so your Estate Plan can be Later our role helps to simplify the process by aiding your personal representative with the location and management of your As well as assisting in any type of estate distribution and For a free brochure on Trust Planning click here Want To Learn How To Create Your Estate Plan? We often start or end team meetings with an honest, “How’s everybody doing?” Creating and fostering a safe, trusting environment where it’s ok to talk about what’s really going on can do wonders for your team whether there’s an outbreak going on or Keep a Regular Schedule Now that you’re not out fighting traffic to get to work, you might have extra time to work out, meditate, read, or your morning routine to make good use of the Block out your work day to keep some Plan Your Workdays Set goals and maintain a list for your days and Don’t stress if you don’t get everything Just keep refocusing every day on the most important things for that Create a Productive Workspace If you can set aside a dedicated home office space, that’s But with everybody staying home that might not work for Create a comfortable corner , keep things uncluttered, use headphones , use a bedroom to try to reduce Take Breaks Give yourself a regular lunch break and other breaks during the Set a time limit and stick with Even with social distancing, you can go outside to take a walk and get some sunlight and fresh air . Getting up and walking around is a better break than taking minutes to surf the Don’t Obsess Over the News Yes, there are “Breaking News” developments all the But don’t let news watching turn you into a Shut off email and text Set a time to get news updates and stick with When you’re working, try just to focus on Use Tech to Stay Connected At GMN, we use a lot of tools to stay We We We We do video conference And we use group collaboration Don’t underestimate the value of seeing the faces of your – even if it’s just video , it’s encouraging to see your friends and More On GMN What is the Global Mentor Network? FAQs (Frequently Asked Questions) | RALOS Home Services All Services Electrical Services Solar Services HVAC Services Generator Services Efficiency Optimizations About Solar Process Blog FAQs The Team Careers Our Team Referrals Free Quote Frequently Asked Questions As we have helped hundreds of customers, many of the same questions come up and particularly in solar, there can be a lot of wrong information out Here we hope to keep an updated list of the questions we get the most often as well as questions that we see a lot of wrong information out there If you have a question that you can t find listed here, please give us a call and one of our team members will do their best to get it answered for you! Read Our Most: Asked Questions Give Us a Call: (208) SPECIAL OFFER! Request your FREE Solar Quote today! Licenses: ID • ID • AZ #341976 Our Top Questions We hope that you can find your question listed below, but if you don t see it, please give us a call at (208) or send us a message any time! Is Solar Expensive? Actually, thanks to the push towards renewable energy through both local and federal initiatives, it is cheaper to create your own electricity than it is to buy your power from the Utility You can get Solar with no cost and begin saving money the day your system is turned on! The types of programs and sun exposure will determine how much money you actually My Utility Bill is already Does Solar still make sense? According to information collected by the Energy Information Administration ( ), Residential Utility Rates in Nevada have nearly doubled in the last So even if your bill seems low now, lowering your electric costs through Solar and protecting your rate always makes Do I have to wait until I have a new roof? Since we warranty and insure all of our roof penetrations, we will be the first to tell you if you need a new roof prior to installing a solar The good news is that, in many cases, you can even include the new roof with your Solar project with little or no money out of your pocket! What if the technology gets better in the future? Solar technology is better now than it has ever With today’s technology, there is enough open area and sunshine in the Southwestern to power the entire world! The average increase in a home’s efficiency greatly exceeds any loss of efficiency in the Solar panels, which means a system that is creating all of your electricity today should continue to do so for the lifetime of the Plus, as State and Federal incentives continue to decline over the next several years, the overall cost for Solar is likely to What if I decide to sell my home? All of the Solar financing programs we work on are fully transferable when you decide to sell your Not only that, recent studies show that Solar panels will actually increase the value of your home and help your home sell quicker! In most cases, a home with Solar will see 3 or 4 different owners during the initial lifespan of the equipment, all of whom will benefit from the power being created Will it cause my roof to leak when it rains? Every system is professionally installed and weather Each installation includes a roof penetration warranty and a separate insurance policy which covers not only the roof itself, but everything inside your home as well! Solar has been known to extend the life of the roof it is covering because the panels will absorb most of the weather and harmful elements that typically break down your roof material, which means you will typically get more life out of your roof than you would without rooftop Solar Do I have to lease the system? No! We have a variety of different options, which allows us to tailor each system based off what is the best fit for you and your We will explore all of the different incentives and programs you may be eligible for and make sure you understand how the programs Solar is not a “one-size-fits-all” When you schedule your no cost, no obligation Solar Consultation, we will explore all of the various options and let you decide what makes the most sense for your Will I be able to create all of the power I use? In most cases, we are able to produce % of the electricity your home currently Each home is different, however, so we will take a look at your usage and even look at other energy saving options that can help save you money! If you are currently connected to the local utility, you may still have to pay a connection fee and certain government taxes once your system is turned on, but creating your power through Solar is still much cheaper since the bulk of your utility cost comes from the electricity you purchase from the Utility! Where are you able to install solar? We are constantly expanding where we can bring our unique energy solutions so if your state isn t highlighted below, make sure to check back Start Your Solar Adventure Today Design Your Own System Usitlize our custom design tools and process to help you create your own solar system, Shop Now Get A Professional Design

About SmartPatch - SmartPatch Skip to content ABOUT CONTACT GET A QUOTE INDUSTRIES BLOG CLIENT LOGIN (800) About SmartPatch Matt :04:11+00:00 The SmartPatch Story One day, while in his dimly lit laboratory, with smooth jazz streaming in the background, Rich “Dr. Patch” Soergel, was staring at the thousands of Patches that he’s created over the years and wondered aloud, “How can we take our custom Patch & Emblem business to the next level?” With various patents and trademarks under his belt, the lightbulb went off while sipping on his favorite Arnold “What if we invented a patch that could ‘talk’ to consumers giving them information on a brands products or services and then have the consumer interact back with the brand? What if we were able to harness today’s technology and morph it into a Patch, in a way that websites, videos, coupons, offers and more could all be accessed simply by using your Well, as often is the case in creativity, the first ideas sometimes fall short, and the same held true for the (Remember, Colonel Sanders finally got his Chicken recipe out to market after tries at the age of ). So, with some deeper thought and determination, Patch went from idea to reality and SmartPatch was on its Many fabrications, samples, testing and ideas were worked through over the next year – patents and trademarks were applied for – the SmartPatch App was created and implemented and the final design and technology that we have today is now available for “Phew…we did it!”, Rich joyfully blurted out with a big (a special thanks to Chris for keeping Rich motivated and brainstorming in the early stages). Seeing the vast landscape ahead with opportunities and industries needing a new and powerful Branded Engagement System (BES), Patch sought out the advice of colleagues and industry leaders to help guide the next steps for Eventually bringing a longtime friend, Steve Thompson, the wizard of scaling and managing a brand onto the team and making him the head of ” From there the team continued to grow and is actively building each and every day, with new enthusiasm and a quest for making SmartPatch every bit of that early dream that the Doctor Imagine the Possibilities! national police chief charged in New York – News Corp Daily Skip to content News Corp Daily Series Of Conglomerate Domain Primary Menu News Corp Daily Search for: Home Uncategorized national police chief charged in New York National Uncategorized national police chief charged in New York 7 months ago News Corp Spread the love The former chief of the Honduran National Police has been charged in New York with drug and weapons crimes … Spread the love The former chief of the Honduran National Police has been charged in New York with drug and weapons crimes By CLAUDIA TORRENS, CHRISTOPHER SHERMAN and MARLON GONZALEZ Associated Press April , , 8:08 PM 4 min read 4 min read NEW YORK — The former chief of the Honduran National Police faces drug and weapons charges in New York, where prosecutors claimed Thursday that he traded his law enforcement clout to protect shipments of The charges were brought against Juan Carlos Bonilla Valladares, known as “El Tigre” or “The Tiger,” in Manhattan federal He was not in Manhattan Attorney Geoffrey Berman said Bonilla played a key role in a violent international drug conspiracy, working on behalf of former Honduran congressman Tony Hernández Alvarado and, his brother, Honduran President Juan Orlando “Bonilla Valladares oversaw the transshipment of loads of cocaine bound for the , used machineguns and other weaponry to accomplish that, and participated in extreme violence, including the murder of a rival trafficker,” Berman said in a Wendy Woolcock, a Drug Enforcement Administration official, said Bonilla’s protection of politically connected drug traffickers “was a blatant and horrific violation” of his Bonilla, , told local press in Honduras Thursday that he’d done nothing “I feel my dignity has been completely offended because I am not a drug trafficker,” Bonilla told “When I was director I didn’t take orders from any ” He said he would go wherever necessary to prove the accusations untrue and suggested drug traffickers were behind the He held up his long cooperation with the State Department as proof he was someone the government “I have not been, nor will be a conspirator with someone accused of drug trafficking,” he “I say it with the respect I have for the president (Hernández), everyone answers for their I never have been involved with him or his ” Bonilla was named head of Honduras’ National Police in May by President Porfirio Lobo said Thursday he brought Bonilla in to clean up the force, because he was known as a straight “I never knew anything about him related to (drug trafficking),” Lobo Authorities said the drug trafficking conspiracy stretched from until this year as drug peddling organizations in Honduras and elsewhere teamed up with prominent public and private individuals, including Honduran politicians and law enforcement It’s not the first time prosecutors have linked President Hernández to the drug Last August, prosecutors said he had used $1.5 million from drug traffickers to help win the presidency in The president has not been charged and he did not immediately comment on the allegations through a spokesman Thursday, but he has repeatedly denied similar allegations Prosecutors said Bonilla let drug shipments pass through police checkpoints without inspection and gave drug organizations information about police aerial and maritime interdiction operations so they could evade An internal police report in Honduras once accused Bonilla of leading death squads and participating in three killings or forced disappearances between and He was prosecuted for one murder but was acquitted in Dana Frank, a history professor at the University of California Santa Cruz who has written extensively about Honduras’ corruption and the government’s
